    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Stance)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You concentrate, simulating a drunken state of mind to make your movements difficult to read. You can Feint in combat as a move action, and gain a +1 dodge bonus to Defense. You are not granted any bonuses if you wield any weapons, unless you have the ability to make those weapons be treated as unarmed attacks.<br><br>If you are actually drunk, reduce the Skill Threshold by 1 and the Perform DC by 5.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step has the stance grant a +1 bonus to attack rolls.</p>\n",
